reviewText:
Never Ending Story was my first best movie growing up in the 80s. I've never seen any fantasy as fun as this movie and I've watch a lot. I can never get tire of watching this classic. I really recommended.

(Espanol)

La Historia Sin Fin es mi primera, mejor pelicula cuando estaba cresiendo en los anos 80s. Nunca e visto una pelicula de fantasia tan divertida como esta y yo e visto muchas. Nunca me canso de verla. Yo se lo recomiendo.
